<item>
            <title>[DERBY-6990] Fix the release notes generator now that the JIRA SOAP api has been deprecated</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/DERBY-6990</link>
                <project id="10594" key="DERBY">Derby</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;The current version of JIRA no longer supports the SOAP api used by the release notes generator to list fixed bugs, their summaries, and detailed release notes. We need to fix this tool before we can produce any more releases.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
                <environment></environment>
