[ &lt;a href=&quot;https://svn.apache.org/r1827682&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;https://svn.apache.org/r1827682&lt;/a&gt; ]&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/DERBY-6990&quot; title=&quot;Fix the release notes generator now that the JIRA SOAP api has been deprecated&quot; class=&quot;issue-link&quot; data-issue-key=&quot;DERBY-6990&quot;&gt;DERBY-6990&lt;/a&gt;: Port 1827681 from trunk to the 10.14 branch.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="16464810" author="bryanpendleton" created="Sat, 5 May 2018 15:22:37 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Other than possibly improving the wiki pages, I think we&apos;re done with this? Rick, you could probably resolve this, unless you want to keep working on it &lt;img class=&quot;emoticon&quot; src=&quot;https://issues.apache.org/jira/images/icons/emoticons/smile.png&quot; height=&quot;16&quot; width=&quot;16&quot; align=&quot;absmiddle&quot; alt=&quot;&quot; border=&quot;0&quot;/&gt;&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="16464858" author="rhillegas" created="Sat, 5 May 2018 18:27:31 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Thanks, Bryan. I&apos;ll keep this open for a while in case I have some ideas about how to improve the generation of the list of issues.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
